                      </svg>                 
                  <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold mt-2">Validated Services</h5>   
                  <p>The service requests are validated with set of pre-defined rules which categorizes if the request is approved or not for further execution. This acts as a confirmation before actual execution is performed.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </a>  
          </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>